Bluebird garage Christmas Market: Find food, clothes and kitschs from local designers and traders to gift to loved ones this weekend at this family and pet friendly Christmas garage market. Details: The market will take place on December 15 at the Blue Bird Garage market, 39 Albertyn Road, Muizenberg, Cape Town.
