 Small. The programme also includes a fashion show featuring fashion houses Mantsho, Fred Eboka, Maxhosa, Imprint and Linda Sithole. Details: The festival takes place on December 13 and 15 at the Buffalo Park Cricket Stadium, Hamilton Sports Club, 1 Clevedon Road, Selborne, East London. The fashion show takes place at the Hemingways Mall, corner Western Avenue & Two Rivers Drive, Cambridge Village, East London. Tickets cost R250 and can be purchased from Computicket. For more information visit www.buyelekhaya.co.za